        public T asOf(String wallclockTime)
       throws FeatureStoreException,
              ParseException
        Perform time travel on the given Query. This method returns a new Query object at the specified point in time. This can then either be read into a Dataframe or used further to perform joins or construct a training dataset.
        Parameters:
        wallclockTime - point in time
        Returns:
        Query
        Throws:
        FeatureStoreException
        ParseException
